# neopub

## Usage

To run a local server, `cd servers/node && yarn start`.

To point the client at that, `echo "REACT_APP_HOST_PREFIX=http://localhost:8888" > frontend/.env.local && cd frontend && yarn start`.

To post from the CLI, 
1. run the web server and client,
1. create an ID,
1. save credentials to a file (`id.json`),
1. put that file in the `cli` directory,
1. `cd cli`
1. `yarn`
1. `echo "your message" | yarn cli`.
